    "description": {
      "desc_thousand_char": "Godrej Properties Limited (GPL), as per its credit rating report, is the real estate venture of the Godrej Group. The company has undertaken projects such as Godrej BKC, Godrej Eternia, Godrej Central, Godrej City, Godrej Emerald, Godrej Eternity, Godrej Exquisite, and Godrej Forest Grove, among others. GPL has delivered 22 million sq. ft. of real estate and currently has around 186 MSF of saleable area spread across 84 projects. GPL has a projects located in Noida, Bengaluru, Delhi, Pune, Kolkata, Sonipat, Nagpur, Indore, and Vadodara, among others."
